pipe (specs_tests4)

 o: faninany |
    sort |
    specs 2-* 1 |
    cons ?

-- specs X2C  ?
   specs /4b3A5b/ x2c 1 |
   c1: compare any ~2# 1 specs X2c ~ equal ~*OK*~ notequal ~**FAIL**  at rec \\c col \\b.~ less /Less:\nActual:\n\\p\nExpected:\n\\s\n/ more /More:\nActual:\n\\p\nExpected:\n\\s\n/ |
   o: ?
   literal K:[ |
   c1: ?

